page.title: 09Westhill Community Centre.
page.content:
These{clubs}all take place at Westhill Community Centre : Badminton ,Boy's Brigade,Bridge,Brownies ,Computer Club, Dance Club,Dressmaking ,Football coaching,Furniture Renovation, Gymnastics,Mother and Toddler, Motor Car Maintenence ,Motorcycle Maintenence,Netball ,Photography Class, Playgroup,Pop Mobility,Senior Youth Club,Women's Group,and Yoga.
MONDAY-12 clubs THURSDAY-6 clubs TUESDAY-9 clubs FRIDAY-7 clubs WEDNESDAY-7 clubs
The clubs take place in these rooms, Activity Room,Creche Room,Practice Hall,Library,Gymnasium,Dining room and the Dance studio.
